# Only version Unity source folders from Reloader/
Reloader/*
!Reloader/Assets/
!Reloader/Packages/
!Reloader/ProjectSettings/
!Reloader/Assets/**
!Reloader/Packages/**
!Reloader/ProjectSettings/**

